elements.long_description: Another Hario product in our store. This is a classic, but it takes a little while to master. The results, however, are more than worth it. Perfect when you want a specialty device that allows you to experiment with different techniques, tastes, and strengths in a novel way. Your friends will think you're a born alchemist.
